chat_history: JESSE: We got some shit to discuss.
Narrator: Buzz, to Jesse, unintimidated:
BUZZ: Ain't got nothin' to say to you, Wheeler.
LONG-HAIR: (top of his lungs) I need a doctor! I need a fuckin' doctor!

Narrator: In one motion, Jesse racks the shotgun, thrusts the barrel to Long-Hair's chin AND BLOWS HIS HEAD OFF. Buzz screams, REARS UP, chair collapses beneath him, DRAGGING a dead Long-Hair along the floor, still tied together.
JESSE: House call.
Narrator: Jesse YANKS Buzz up. His chair rocks upright, into place.
JESSE: Where's Lucian?!
BUZZ: I don't know!
Narrator: Jesse punctuates, shotgun butt against Buzz's head. Necksnaps. Teeth rattle.
Narrator: Jesse strikes again, connects. Buzz goes down in a heap, eyesswollen purple slits. His skull gushing red.
BUZZ: ...fuck...
Narrator: Jesse steps over Buzz, pins the shotgun to his jaw.
JESSE: Who killed my family?
BUZZ: Ah shit, man!
Narrator: Jesse shifts his aim an inch, pulls the trigger. SHOT REVERBSHARD. Buzz SCREAMS, hysteria.
JESSE: (racks another shell)
Narrator: Jesse puts down the shotgun. Pulls from his gym bag, two CANSOF GASOLINE, one of which, he splashes over Buzz's face.
BUZZ: (flinches) The fuck is that? (sniffs, realizes)
Narrator: Jesse pours the rest over Buzz and the lifeless Long-Hair.
BUZZ: (thrashing)
Narrator: As Buzz pleads for his life, Jesse unloads the shotgun, deadaim...FIRES.
